#: model_terms:forum.forum,faq:website_slides_forum.forum_forum_demo_channel_2
msgid "specific questions about Odoo service offers, etc."
msgstr "ຄຳຖາມສະເພາະກ່ຽວກັບການບໍລິການຂອງ Odoo, ແລະ ອື່ນໆ."

#. module: website_slides_forum
#: model_terms:forum.forum,faq:website_slides_forum.forum_forum_demo_channel_0
#: model_terms:forum.forum,faq:website_slides_forum.forum_forum_demo_channel_2
msgid ""
"there is no actual problem to be solved: “I’m curious if other people feel "
"like I do.”"
msgstr ""
"ບໍ່ມີບັນຫາຕົວຈິງທີ່ຕ້ອງແກ້ໄຂ: “ຂ້ອຍຢາກຮູ້ວ່າຄົນອື່ນຮູ້ສຶກຄືກັນກັບຂ້ອຍບໍ່.”"

#. module: website_slides_forum
#: model_terms:forum.forum,faq:website_slides_forum.forum_forum_demo_channel_0
#: model_terms:forum.forum,faq:website_slides_forum.forum_forum_demo_channel_2
msgid ""
"we are being asked an open-ended, hypothetical question: “What if ______ "
"happened?”"
msgstr "ພວກເຮົາຖືກຖາມຄຳຖາມປາຍເປີດ ຫຼື ຄຳຖາມສົມມຸດ: “ຈະເກີດຫຍັງຂຶ້ນ ຖ້າ ______?”"

#. module: website_slides_forum
#: model_terms:forum.forum,faq:website_slides_forum.forum_forum_demo_channel_0
#: model_terms:forum.forum,faq:website_slides_forum.forum_forum_demo_channel_2
msgid "what's the best way to use Odoo for a specific business need,"
msgstr "ວິທີທີ່ດີທີ່ສຸດໃນການໃຊ້ Odoo ສຳລັບຄວາມຕ້ອງການທາງທຸລະກິດສະເພາະ,"

#. module: website_slides_forum
#: model_terms:forum.forum,faq:website_slides_forum.forum_forum_demo_channel_0
#: model_terms:forum.forum,faq:website_slides_forum.forum_forum_demo_channel_2
msgid ""
"your answer is provided along with the question, and you expect more "
"answers: “I use ______ for ______, what do you use?”"
msgstr ""
"ຄຳຕອບຂອງທ່ານຖືກໃຫ້ມາພ້ອມກັບຄຳຖາມ, ແລະ ທ່ານຄາດຫວັງວ່າຈະໄດ້ຮັບຄຳຕອບເພີ່ມເຕີມ: “ຂ້ອຍໃຊ້ ______ "
"ສຳລັບ ______, ແລ້ວເຈົ້າເດໃຊ້ຫຍັງ?”"
